1
00:00:16,530 --> 00:00:19,300
Lucy-san! Are you awake?!

2
00:00:19,860 --> 00:00:21,750
Which match is it right now?

3
00:00:21,750 --> 00:00:24,250
The first match just finished.

4
00:00:24,590 --> 00:00:26,800
It looks like Blue Pegasus won.

5
00:00:26,800 --> 00:00:29,410
The second match is just about to begin.

6
00:00:29,410 --> 00:00:31,760
It's between Lamia Scale and Mermaid Heel.

7
00:00:32,140 --> 00:00:35,580
I see... Then Natsu and the 
others' match hasn't started yet.

8
00:00:35,580 --> 00:00:40,250
Natsu-san said he'd come and 
see you before his match.

9
00:00:40,250 --> 00:00:43,600
Rest up a little more until then.

10
00:00:43,990 --> 00:00:47,490
It's important for you to 
get your strength back.

11
00:00:47,800 --> 00:00:50,080
Thank you. I will.

12
00:02:23,950 --> 00:02:26,790
Alright! The second match is next.

13
00:02:26,790 --> 00:02:28,460
From Lamia Scale,

14
00:02:28,930 --> 00:02:31,070
Lyon and Yuka!

15
00:02:32,390 --> 00:02:35,330
And from Mermaid Heel,

16
00:02:35,590 --> 00:02:38,150
Kagura and Millianna are competing!

17
00:02:38,150 --> 00:02:40,380
Feelin' spiffy!

18
00:02:40,620 --> 00:02:42,890
Let's feel the love for Mermaid Heel!

19
00:02:43,410 --> 00:02:46,470
Yajima-san, what are your 
thoughts on this match?

20
00:02:46,730 --> 00:02:49,180
I wouldn't be surprised if either side won.

21
00:02:49,180 --> 00:02:51,550
I'm certainly looking forward to this match.

22
00:02:51,550 --> 00:02:53,420
Both Lyon and Yuka are strong opponents!

23
00:02:53,420 --> 00:02:55,750
Millianna! Don't let your guard down!

24
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:59,240
Are you rooting for Mermaid Heel?

25
00:02:59,450 --> 00:03:02,780
Yeah. We've known each other a long time.

26
00:03:02,780 --> 00:03:05,700
It's only natural that 
I'd want to support her.

27
00:03:06,070 --> 00:03:10,300
Gray, you've known Lyon 
for a long time, right?

28
00:03:10,300 --> 00:03:11,800
Aren't you interested in this?

29
00:03:12,110 --> 00:03:13,400
Not really.

30
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:16,670
We're in different guilds now and are rivals.

31
00:03:20,480 --> 00:03:21,910
What's wrong, Natsu?

32
00:03:23,370 --> 00:03:27,680
I was thinking that Lucy and Elfman would 
probably like to see the matches, too.

33
00:03:29,910 --> 00:03:33,180
In that case, let's watch 
it carefully for them.

34
00:03:33,460 --> 00:03:35,310
So we can tell them about it later.

35
00:03:36,210 --> 00:03:37,710
Guess you're right...

36
00:03:38,210 --> 00:03:40,480
Alright! I'll do it.

37
00:03:43,050 --> 00:03:45,920
Battle of the Dragon Slayers!

38
00:03:48,730 --> 00:03:51,680
I hope Mermaid Heel wins.

39
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:55,210
I've known Millianna since that 
Tower of Heaven business, see.

40
00:03:55,210 --> 00:03:57,800
I guess I'm rooting for Lamia Scale.

41
00:03:57,800 --> 00:04:00,310
They've been a big help.

42
00:04:00,310 --> 00:04:03,760
Certainly, we have a history 
with Lamia Scale...

43
00:04:03,970 --> 00:04:08,480
...but all of the Mermaid Heel 
wizards are beauties, right?

44
00:04:10,850 --> 00:04:13,310
Juvia, I guess you're cheering for Lyon, huh?

45
00:04:13,310 --> 00:04:15,970
You've been approached by 
Lyon more than once, right?

46
00:04:15,970 --> 00:04:18,880
Having a woman's heart, you 
must be interested, right?

47
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:22,070
Juvia... Juvia...

48
00:04:22,650 --> 00:04:27,430
...wanted to stay on the team and 
battle alongside Gray-sama...

49
00:04:29,200 --> 00:04:32,150
That's it! There's still a chance!

50
00:04:32,150 --> 00:04:36,240
If someone on the team gets injured during 
the match, and they become short a person...

51
00:04:38,910 --> 00:04:42,310
I knew that you were the only partner for me!

52
00:04:42,310 --> 00:04:43,260
Kiss!

53
00:04:44,740 --> 00:04:45,810
Juvia...

54
00:04:47,430 --> 00:04:49,730
I'm overjoyed, Gray-sama!

55
00:04:50,430 --> 00:04:51,900
No!

56
00:04:51,900 --> 00:04:56,660
As a member of the guild, Juvia is a bad 
girl for wishing injuries on her comrades!

57
00:04:57,170 --> 00:04:59,570
But Juvia wants to be by Gray-sama's side!

58
00:04:59,570 --> 00:05:03,260
And yet...! Juvia doesn't want 
her guildmates to get hurt!

59
00:05:03,260 --> 00:05:05,230
What should Juvia do?!

60
00:05:05,230 --> 00:05:07,430
W-What's wrong, Juvia?

61
00:05:07,430 --> 00:05:09,150
Is there something on your mind?

62
00:05:09,150 --> 00:05:13,290
We'll give you good counsel, so 
go ahead and share with us girls.

63
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:16,920
After this match is over,

64
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:21,300
the next one is between Fairy 
Tail and Sabertooth at last.

65
00:05:21,300 --> 00:05:23,750
All we need to do is have faith in them.

66
00:05:23,750 --> 00:05:26,170
Let's take a load off and wait...

67
00:05:28,310 --> 00:05:29,800
First Master!

68
00:05:30,270 --> 00:05:33,850
Everyone, make sure you 
look before you sit down.

69
00:05:38,280 --> 00:05:39,530
Maybe...

70
00:05:39,530 --> 00:05:43,320
...Jellal is watching this 
match from the stands...

71
00:05:44,410 --> 00:05:45,740
Millianna...

72
00:05:46,410 --> 00:05:47,610
Focus.

73
00:05:48,150 --> 00:05:49,430
I know!

74
00:05:50,910 --> 00:05:54,130
At first, try fighting 
this match on your own.

75
00:05:54,330 --> 00:05:56,290
I'm going to hold back for a while.

76
00:05:56,290 --> 00:05:58,280
I don't believe this! Why?!

77
00:05:58,280 --> 00:06:00,050
So you can gain experience...

78
00:06:00,290 --> 00:06:03,080
Match or not, this is a real fight.

79
00:06:03,380 --> 00:06:05,840
How far can you battle 
with just your own power?

80
00:06:06,330 --> 00:06:08,140
You should try it.

81
00:06:08,140 --> 00:06:10,700
Alright. I will!

82
00:06:11,050 --> 00:06:13,180
Our opponents are two women.

83
00:06:13,180 --> 00:06:16,990
But if we don't go all out against those 
two, it's doubtful that we'll achieve victory.

84
00:06:16,990 --> 00:06:18,980
That's because Kagura is one of them.

85
00:06:19,500 --> 00:06:23,130
But if I strut my stuff for her...

86
00:06:24,410 --> 00:06:26,650
...I'm sure she'll think more highly of me!

87
00:06:26,650 --> 00:06:29,110
Hey, that might be a little cocky...

88
00:06:29,540 --> 00:06:33,990
Hey! If you don't do this right, 
I'll make the both of you spin!

89
00:06:33,990 --> 00:06:36,660
The time limit is 30 minutes!

90
00:06:36,660 --> 00:06:39,920
Alright, let the match begin-kabo!

91
00:06:40,500 --> 00:06:43,170
Victory goes to the swiftest!

92
00:06:44,230 --> 00:06:46,300
Cat Binding Tube!

93
00:06:50,050 --> 00:06:52,900
Is Millianna fighting alone?!

94
00:06:52,900 --> 00:06:55,740
Will she be okay against 
opponents from Lamia Scale?

95
00:06:56,010 --> 00:06:58,310
Kagura must have figured 
she'd be able to handle it.

96
00:06:58,790 --> 00:07:00,990
Let's leave it to her judgment.

97
00:07:02,760 --> 00:07:05,010
Kagura-chan doesn't need to take part!

98
00:07:06,590 --> 00:07:09,390
They're really making light of us...

99
00:07:09,390 --> 00:07:11,600
They must be confident...

100
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:15,280
You... Mermaid Heel...

101
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:19,260
Lyon! Yuka! Do whatever 
you have to do to win!

102
00:07:19,260 --> 00:07:22,480
Show them how strong we are!

103
00:07:23,250 --> 00:07:25,320
Kagura is just watching?

104
00:07:25,320 --> 00:07:27,920
In that case, let's drag her to the party!

105
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:30,170
Ice Make: Eagle!

106
00:07:33,950 --> 00:07:35,720
Don't ignore me!

107
00:07:36,070 --> 00:07:38,060
Wave!

108
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:42,210
She's fast!

109
00:07:42,500 --> 00:07:44,600
Kitten Blast!

110
00:07:47,990 --> 00:07:48,860
A fake-out, huh?

111
00:07:49,100 --> 00:07:50,610
Gotcha!

112
00:07:50,820 --> 00:07:52,820
Cat punch! Cat punch! Punch!

113
00:07:52,820 --> 00:07:54,100
There it is!

114
00:07:54,100 --> 00:07:57,450
The first attack that's 
landed is by Mermaid Heel!

115
00:07:57,450 --> 00:07:59,350
Great! You're cookin' with gas!

116
00:07:59,350 --> 00:08:01,530
She's totally relaxed as she fights.

117
00:08:01,900 --> 00:08:05,000
Maybe it's because she feels 
secure with Kagura behind her.

118
00:08:07,370 --> 00:08:09,680
You ain't seen nothin' yet!

119
00:08:10,060 --> 00:08:13,510
I train with Kagura-chan every day!

120
00:08:15,590 --> 00:08:16,990
Secret weapon!

121
00:08:18,530 --> 00:08:20,270
Scratch attack!

122
00:08:20,270 --> 00:08:23,560
What's wrong? You're not 
putting up any resistance!

123
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:26,520
This is a surprise!

124
00:08:26,520 --> 00:08:31,410
Those two are the go-to wizards of Lamia 
Scale, but Millianna isn't giving an inch!

125
00:08:31,410 --> 00:08:33,830
It seems that both of her 
opponents are flummoxed

126
00:08:33,830 --> 00:08:36,410
by her quick, cat-like moves.

127
00:08:36,410 --> 00:08:39,840
Ow... That girl is better than I thought...

128
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:42,520
If she weren't, it wouldn't be interesting!

129
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:45,050
Cat Binding Tube!

130
00:08:45,250 --> 00:08:45,990
But...

131
00:08:47,900 --> 00:08:51,550
...my wave can nullify magic attacks!

132
00:08:51,980 --> 00:08:54,690
Huh. In that case, how's this?!

133
00:08:54,690 --> 00:08:56,560
Cat Binding Tube!

134
00:08:56,560 --> 00:08:59,050
Double! Triple! Uh...

135
00:09:00,750 --> 00:09:02,060
A lot!

136
00:09:02,280 --> 00:09:04,310
So you can produce several at once, huh?

137
00:09:04,550 --> 00:09:06,850
My techniques are evolving, too!

138
00:09:13,270 --> 00:09:15,370
Ice Make: Eagle!

139
00:09:15,660 --> 00:09:17,040
She's doing it again!

140
00:09:17,040 --> 00:09:18,820
You're just wasting your energy!

141
00:09:25,900 --> 00:09:28,700
Well? How about giving up?

142
00:09:28,700 --> 00:09:29,890
This is no good...

143
00:09:29,890 --> 00:09:33,730
At this rate, I won't be able 
to look cool in front of Juvia!

144
00:09:34,010 --> 00:09:36,340
Hey, you're still worried about that?

145
00:09:36,340 --> 00:09:37,550
But...

146
00:09:38,100 --> 00:09:41,150
...I have brains as well as techniques!

147
00:09:41,150 --> 00:09:43,900
This is the only thing to 
do against a cat opponent!

148
00:09:43,900 --> 00:09:46,540
Ice Make: Mouse!

149
00:09:51,650 --> 00:09:54,800
A mouse! Whee!

150
00:09:54,800 --> 00:09:56,350
Wait for me!

151
00:09:58,140 --> 00:10:00,010
Don't insult my intelligence!

152
00:10:00,560 --> 00:10:02,490
Next up is this!

153
00:10:03,330 --> 00:10:04,990
Blow, blizzard!

154
00:10:06,570 --> 00:10:08,750
I-It's cold...

155
00:10:10,120 --> 00:10:13,330
Cats don't like winter...

156
00:10:13,790 --> 00:10:15,380
A <i>kotatsu</i>!

157
00:10:16,250 --> 00:10:20,180
Cats love <i>kotatsus</i>...

158
00:10:20,570 --> 00:10:22,600
It's comfy and warm...

159
00:10:26,340 --> 00:10:28,940
Would you stop treating me like a cat?!

160
00:10:29,610 --> 00:10:32,910
I didn't think they'd trick Millianna 
with that kind of method!

161
00:10:32,910 --> 00:10:36,840
That's Lyon of Lamia Scale for you. 
You can't be too cautious with him.

162
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:40,550
Um... Are you guys really that impressed?

163
00:10:40,900 --> 00:10:44,990
Did you see that, Juvia? 
My beautiful brain play!

164
00:10:49,090 --> 00:10:50,330
She's turned off...

165
00:10:51,700 --> 00:10:53,580
Lyon Vastia...

166
00:10:53,820 --> 00:10:56,830
You haven't directly attacked Millianna yet.

167
00:10:56,830 --> 00:10:58,700
Great! Great!

168
00:10:58,700 --> 00:11:03,200
This is a tough battle for both 
Mermaid Heel and Lamia Scale!

169
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:05,550
Kabo! Kabo! Kabo!

170
00:11:05,550 --> 00:11:09,560
Hey! Lyon and Yuka, quit standing around!

171
00:11:09,560 --> 00:11:12,310
If you don't win this right 
now, I'm gonna make you spin!

172
00:11:12,310 --> 00:11:14,610
What happens if you get spun?

173
00:11:14,610 --> 00:11:16,610
I can't really describe it,

174
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:20,110
but anyway, it's really bad for sure!

175
00:11:20,110 --> 00:11:21,680
Obaba's right.

176
00:11:21,680 --> 00:11:25,630
At this rate, we're gonna run out of the 
30-minute time limit and it'll be a draw.

177
00:11:25,630 --> 00:11:27,050
Then I have no choice.

178
00:11:27,050 --> 00:11:29,910
I intended to save Kagura for last, but...

179
00:11:29,910 --> 00:11:33,370
Ice Make: Snow Tiger!

180
00:11:39,290 --> 00:11:42,070
I love cats, but tigers are another thing!

181
00:11:48,450 --> 00:11:50,880
Kagura-chan... I'm sorry...

182
00:11:51,700 --> 00:11:55,020
I suppose I have to participate after all...

183
00:11:56,610 --> 00:11:59,250
So you've finally decided to play, Kagura!

184
00:11:59,250 --> 00:12:00,630
I'll go first!

185
00:12:00,960 --> 00:12:02,070
Wave!

186
00:12:05,630 --> 00:12:08,400
An attack that nullifies 
your opponent's magic, eh?

187
00:12:08,400 --> 00:12:09,380
However...

188
00:12:11,760 --> 00:12:14,500
...it's meaningless if your opponent 
doesn't use magic attacks!

189
00:12:16,880 --> 00:12:18,970
Good heavens!

190
00:12:18,970 --> 00:12:20,950
Mermaid Heel's Kagura...

191
00:12:20,950 --> 00:12:24,800
...is overpowering her opponent 
with her sheathed sword!

192
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:26,770
Wave!

193
00:12:29,620 --> 00:12:30,520
You're slow!

194
00:12:36,750 --> 00:12:38,100
Incredible!

195
00:12:38,100 --> 00:12:42,000
She's downed Yuka by not giving 
him a moment to retaliate!

196
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:43,900
At last, it's just Kagura and Lyon!

197
00:12:43,900 --> 00:12:45,760
One on one!

198
00:12:56,710 --> 00:12:59,060
She beat one of them without 
even drawing her sword?

199
00:12:59,450 --> 00:13:01,010
Impressive...

200
00:13:01,010 --> 00:13:06,100
Yeah. Kagura is an expert 
with a sheathed sword.

201
00:13:06,100 --> 00:13:09,880
Maybe she'd be a worthy opponent 
for my Iron Dragon Sword.

202
00:13:13,790 --> 00:13:16,640
W-Will Lyon be okay?

203
00:13:16,640 --> 00:13:19,300
Even though he had a hard 
time against Millianna,

204
00:13:19,300 --> 00:13:21,750
going one on one against Kagura...

205
00:13:21,750 --> 00:13:26,150
What? Lyon hasn't unleashed 
his true strength yet.

206
00:13:26,150 --> 00:13:29,580
Lyon! No matter what, you'd better win!

207
00:13:29,580 --> 00:13:32,030
Show her your power!

208
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:35,170
I've heard about you.

209
00:13:35,510 --> 00:13:37,480
You once went by the name "Reitei".

210
00:13:37,480 --> 00:13:41,480
You attempted a dangerous ritual 
in order to fight Deliora.

211
00:13:42,220 --> 00:13:44,220
That was a long time ago.

212
00:13:44,220 --> 00:13:47,180
Now, I'm Lyon, a wizard with Lamia Scale.

213
00:13:47,180 --> 00:13:49,730
Nothing more or less.

214
00:13:49,730 --> 00:13:53,820
But something about you reminds 
me of the way I used to be.

215
00:13:53,820 --> 00:13:58,120
Back when I was driven by hatred 
and had lost sight of something...

216
00:14:00,160 --> 00:14:01,770
Let me ask you one thing.

217
00:14:02,300 --> 00:14:05,180
Why didn't you attack Millianna directly?

218
00:14:05,660 --> 00:14:08,390
Did you hold back because she's a woman?

219
00:14:08,390 --> 00:14:12,280
Or just because you didn't want 
to reveal your strategy to me?

220
00:14:12,280 --> 00:14:13,910
Who knows?

221
00:14:13,910 --> 00:14:16,760
Maybe you'll find out when you fight me!

222
00:14:16,760 --> 00:14:19,170
Ice Make: Dragonfly!

223
00:14:23,100 --> 00:14:25,170
Ice Make: Eagle!

224
00:14:28,060 --> 00:14:30,150
Kagura really is strong!

225
00:14:30,150 --> 00:14:32,770
Is Lyon powerless to do anything?!

226
00:14:33,740 --> 00:14:35,850
What are you doin', Lyon?!

227
00:14:35,850 --> 00:14:38,070
And you were Ur's disciple?!

228
00:14:38,070 --> 00:14:40,800
You're stronger than that!

229
00:14:41,300 --> 00:14:43,910
Get your act together now!

230
00:14:45,750 --> 00:14:47,300
He's right.

231
00:14:47,300 --> 00:14:51,050
Show me what you've <i>really</i> got, Lyon Vastia!

232
00:14:51,050 --> 00:14:54,280
Yeah. And we are running out of time...

233
00:14:55,380 --> 00:14:58,250
Ice Make: Snow Tiger!

234
00:14:59,500 --> 00:15:02,580
Ice Make: Snow Ape!

235
00:15:03,910 --> 00:15:06,750
Ice Make: Snow Dragon!

236
00:15:09,640 --> 00:15:12,730
I bet not even you will 
be able to escape this!

237
00:15:21,550 --> 00:15:23,960
You can create all these at the same time?

238
00:15:24,600 --> 00:15:25,730
Still...

239
00:15:35,270 --> 00:15:38,160
There it is! Her ace in 
the hole, Gravity Change!

240
00:15:38,160 --> 00:15:41,220
Yep! That's Kagura's magic!

241
00:15:41,220 --> 00:15:44,040
Still, for Kagura to use Gravity Change,

242
00:15:44,040 --> 00:15:46,090
it proves that Lyon guy is a tough opponent.

243
00:15:47,090 --> 00:15:48,820
W-What power!

244
00:15:55,500 --> 00:15:57,200
It ends here!

245
00:15:59,140 --> 00:16:02,460
Time's up! 30 minutes have passed!

246
00:16:02,460 --> 00:16:05,310
It's a tie-kabo!

247
00:16:08,440 --> 00:16:10,120
The result is a draw!

248
00:16:10,120 --> 00:16:13,190
It wasn't settled after 30 minutes!

249
00:16:13,190 --> 00:16:15,610
So close!

250
00:16:15,610 --> 00:16:18,120
Just a little more time and 
Lyon would've been toast!

251
00:16:18,330 --> 00:16:20,630
But a tie's a tie.

252
00:16:21,210 --> 00:16:25,210
Ah, well, it looks like Kagura 
isn't too bothered by it...

253
00:16:25,210 --> 00:16:27,850
He squeaked by with a draw.

254
00:16:28,640 --> 00:16:31,140
But what a close call...

255
00:16:31,540 --> 00:16:35,040
This is what happens when 
you've got girls on the mind!

256
00:16:35,040 --> 00:16:39,230
When you get back here, you're 
going to spin and spin and spin!

257
00:16:39,230 --> 00:16:41,270
I'm gonna spin you like never before!

258
00:16:42,060 --> 00:16:44,740
Kagura really is strong, you know?

259
00:16:45,020 --> 00:16:47,640
And I don't think she was 
pulling out all the stops...

260
00:16:47,640 --> 00:16:49,060
It's the same every year.

261
00:16:49,060 --> 00:16:52,990
Nobody's seen Kagura get 
totally serious before.

262
00:16:53,290 --> 00:16:55,530
Kagura-chan, I'm sorry...

263
00:16:56,650 --> 00:16:59,850
That Lyon has natural aptitude.

264
00:16:59,850 --> 00:17:02,810
If this had been a life-or-death 
battle instead of a match,

265
00:17:04,530 --> 00:17:05,980
you'd be dead right now.

266
00:17:08,950 --> 00:17:11,240
Get stronger, Millianna.

267
00:17:11,680 --> 00:17:13,320
I'm going to train you harder.

268
00:17:13,320 --> 00:17:14,530
Right!

269
00:17:14,530 --> 00:17:16,920
The crowd is still pumped 
up here at the arena!

270
00:17:16,920 --> 00:17:19,610
But don't take your eyes 
off of the next battle!

271
00:17:20,060 --> 00:17:21,350
At last!

272
00:17:21,350 --> 00:17:23,000
Yep. At last...

273
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:24,350
At long last!

274
00:17:24,350 --> 00:17:25,220
Finally...

275
00:17:25,220 --> 00:17:26,770
...the time has come!

276
00:17:26,770 --> 00:17:30,080
Natsu-san, Gajeel-kun, don't get hurt!

277
00:17:30,080 --> 00:17:34,700
No injuries! Nobody is allowed to get hurt!

278
00:17:34,700 --> 00:17:37,570
Why are you so obsessed with injuries?

279
00:17:47,800 --> 00:17:49,020
Yo.

280
00:17:49,020 --> 00:17:50,290
How do you feel?

281
00:17:53,400 --> 00:17:55,090
I'm okay.

282
00:17:55,600 --> 00:17:56,930
Is your match next?

283
00:17:56,930 --> 00:17:59,880
Yeah. And I'll win it for sure.

284
00:18:03,880 --> 00:18:04,840
Natsu...

285
00:18:14,340 --> 00:18:18,520
Sorry, Lucy-san! We just went to check 
out what's happening at the arena.

286
00:18:18,520 --> 00:18:19,810
Oh! Natsu?

287
00:18:20,280 --> 00:18:23,200
Wendy, Carla... Take care of her.

288
00:18:23,200 --> 00:18:25,890
Good luck, Natsu-san!

289
00:18:26,340 --> 00:18:29,730
Lucy! What were you talking about with Natsu?

290
00:18:33,710 --> 00:18:35,050
You ready?

291
00:18:35,050 --> 00:18:36,140
Yeah.

292
00:18:36,140 --> 00:18:39,540
Let's make Lucy and the rest 
happy by winnin' this thing.

293
00:18:40,800 --> 00:18:42,010
Natsu!

294
00:18:43,300 --> 00:18:44,520
Happy...

295
00:18:47,280 --> 00:18:51,780
I'm sure all of our viewers have been 
eagerly looking forward to this battle.

296
00:18:55,060 --> 00:18:58,170
A fateful showdown between the 
guild that was called the strongest

297
00:18:58,170 --> 00:19:01,570
seven years ago and the 
strongest current guild!

298
00:19:02,200 --> 00:19:05,050
Fairy Tail's Natsu and Gajeel

299
00:19:05,050 --> 00:19:09,320
versus Sabertooth's Sting and Rogue!

300
00:19:10,240 --> 00:19:13,950
And all four of them are Dragon Slayers.

301
00:19:13,950 --> 00:19:17,420
All four possess anti-dragon magic.

302
00:19:17,980 --> 00:19:19,640
Sting-kun...

303
00:19:20,020 --> 00:19:22,840
I've been waiting for this moment.

304
00:19:27,110 --> 00:19:29,870
The White Dragon, Weisslogia...

305
00:19:29,870 --> 00:19:32,600
The Shadow Dragon, Skiadrum...

306
00:19:32,600 --> 00:19:34,780
Show me...

307
00:19:34,780 --> 00:19:37,480
Have humans surpassed dragons?

308
00:19:40,260 --> 00:19:43,430
Or is that just a fleeting dream?

309
00:19:43,430 --> 00:19:46,390
It is almost time for us to act...

310
00:19:46,390 --> 00:19:49,780
The Festival of the Dragon 
King is almost upon us.

311
00:19:54,250 --> 00:19:58,140
The dream Dragon Slayer 
showdown is finally happening!

312
00:19:58,140 --> 00:19:59,870
Sock it to 'em!

313
00:19:59,870 --> 00:20:01,720
Get 'em for us, too!

314
00:20:01,720 --> 00:20:03,670
I have faith you'll win!

315
00:20:04,560 --> 00:20:06,760
It's about to start.

316
00:20:07,500 --> 00:20:09,350
I'm sure Natsu will be okay.

317
00:20:09,970 --> 00:20:11,250
I'm sure he'll win!

318
00:20:12,420 --> 00:20:14,220
The time to clash is here at last!

319
00:20:14,220 --> 00:20:16,350
Who will win, Fairy or Tiger?!

320
00:20:16,350 --> 00:20:19,880
All four dragons are on the battlefield!

321
00:20:21,180 --> 00:20:25,070
Fight to the best of your ability. 
There's nothing else to say.

322
00:20:27,800 --> 00:20:31,200
I've been waiting years for this, Natsu-san.

323
00:20:37,340 --> 00:20:41,420
I've been looking forward to it, too-kabo!

324
00:20:41,420 --> 00:20:43,670
The time limit is 30 minutes!

325
00:20:43,670 --> 00:20:46,670
Let the match begin!

326
00:20:46,670 --> 00:20:47,460
Here I go!

327
00:20:47,460 --> 00:20:48,500
Yeah!

328
00:20:59,860 --> 00:21:03,060
Roar of the White Dragon!

329
00:21:03,060 --> 00:21:04,280
A laser?!

330
00:21:11,000 --> 00:21:12,740
Slash of the Shadow Dragon!

331
00:21:21,410 --> 00:21:22,430
Rogue!

332
00:21:30,300 --> 00:21:32,750
Wingbeat of the Fire Dragon!

333
00:21:33,510 --> 00:21:36,520
W-What's this?!

334
00:21:36,520 --> 00:21:38,440
Sting and Rogue...

335
00:21:38,440 --> 00:21:42,070
The Twin Dragons of Fiore's 
strongest guild are on the ropes!

336
00:21:43,250 --> 00:21:46,600
He really is strong... But I'd 
be disappointed otherwise.

337
00:21:46,600 --> 00:21:47,570
Gajeel...

338
00:21:48,100 --> 00:21:52,550
Did you two really defeat 
dragons with power like that?

339
00:21:52,550 --> 00:21:54,370
Not defeat...

340
00:21:54,850 --> 00:21:57,690
I killed a dragon with this very hand.

341
00:21:57,990 --> 00:22:00,160
Wasn't it your parent?

342
00:22:00,400 --> 00:22:02,700
It's got nothin' to do with you.

343
00:22:02,990 --> 00:22:06,340
From now, I'm gonna show you 
the power that killed a dragon!

344
00:22:07,450 --> 00:22:09,390
White Drive...

345
00:22:11,600 --> 00:22:13,530
Shadow Drive.

346
00:22:19,440 --> 00:22:20,800
Let's go!

347
00:23:56,140 --> 00:23:58,420
Finally... Finally, it's come!

348
00:23:58,420 --> 00:23:59,450
It's here, huh?

349
00:23:59,450 --> 00:24:00,400
My...

350
00:24:00,400 --> 00:24:01,530
Natsu's...

351
00:24:01,530 --> 00:24:03,940
...time to shine!

352
00:24:03,940 --> 00:24:07,050
I don't know if these guys are new 
generation Dragon Slayers or what,

353
00:24:07,050 --> 00:24:10,300
but I'm gonna kick that blond poser's ass!

354
00:24:10,300 --> 00:24:13,430
Do your best, Natsu!

355
00:24:14,060 --> 00:24:16,430
Next time: Four Dragons!

356
00:24:16,640 --> 00:24:19,760
And then I'm gonna beat up the 
remaining dark-haired duo!

357
00:24:19,760 --> 00:24:21,730
You're including Gajeel...

358
00:24:21,730 --> 00:24:24,160
Ah, whatever... Do your best, Natsu!

